1
00:00:55,240 --> 00:00:58,000
The Princess Consort is now pregnant.

2
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:01,800
Although the fetus can survive,

3
00:01:01,800 --> 00:01:03,560
it will backlash against the mother,

4
00:01:03,560 --> 00:01:06,520
draining her nutrients to stay alive.

5
00:01:07,600 --> 00:01:09,920
The deadly poison in her body

6
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:12,130
will also be transferred to the fetus.

7
00:01:12,320 --> 00:01:13,120
I'm afraid

8
00:01:13,960 --> 00:01:16,200
it will eventually die in the womb,

9
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:19,760
accelerating the mother's death.

10
00:01:25,800 --> 00:01:27,000
Didn't you say before

11
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:28,970
that she could be cured?

12
00:01:30,600 --> 00:01:32,460
Didn't you say she could be cured?

13
00:01:35,080 --> 00:01:36,000
Jingyan.

14
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:41,759
Jingyan.

15
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:04,520
Jingyan.

16
00:02:04,600 --> 00:02:05,920
Why did you lie to me?

17
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:08,560
Why?

18
00:02:11,200 --> 00:02:12,400
If it weren't for you,

19
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:15,840
I would have died countless times.

20
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,079
It was you

21
00:02:21,320 --> 00:02:23,380
who protected me time and time again.

22
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,160
It was you

23
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:30,880
who let me live

24
00:02:30,880 --> 00:02:32,720
to see my revenge fulfilled.

25
00:02:36,440 --> 00:02:37,360
You also let me

26
00:02:38,160 --> 00:02:39,800
experience the deepest love

27
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,800
in this world.

28
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:47,520
Jingyan,

29
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:50,360
the Lingzhi Pool in Yaowang Valley

30
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:55,079
is a place where spiritual energy gathers.

31
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:57,200
It can purge toxins

32
00:02:57,880 --> 00:02:59,079
and nourish life.

33
00:03:00,600 --> 00:03:01,840
I want to try it.

34
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:03,680
For me,

35
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:05,920
and for our child.

36
00:03:06,640 --> 00:03:07,880
I want to live.

37
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:10,170
We'll go to Yaowang Valley right away.

38
00:03:10,880 --> 00:03:11,440
That way,

39
00:03:13,320 --> 00:03:14,980
you and the child will be fine.

40
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:32,400
I'm sorry.

41
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:35,840
It's all my fault.

42
00:03:38,600 --> 00:03:39,760
All my fault.

43
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:21,880
Aunt Qin often said

44
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:24,740
that a healer has the heart of a parent

45
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:26,850
and must always be compassionate.

46
00:04:27,960 --> 00:04:29,890
But why must compassionate people

47
00:04:30,400 --> 00:04:32,000
suffer from injustice?

48
00:04:37,840 --> 00:04:39,040
My mother often said,

49
00:04:40,280 --> 00:04:41,409
if people bully you,

50
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,400
heaven will protect you.

51
00:04:44,880 --> 00:04:46,080
If people betray you,

52
00:04:47,880 --> 00:04:50,400
heaven will repay you.

53
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:04,200
Qingshu.

54
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:08,330
I will always stay by your side,

55
00:05:09,760 --> 00:05:11,240
no matter the outcome.

56
00:05:34,840 --> 00:05:35,640
What's wrong?

57
00:05:59,240 --> 00:05:59,960
Qingshu.

58
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:21,760
You're awake.

59
00:06:31,440 --> 00:06:32,360
Qingshu.

60
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:37,040
It's my fault for not protecting you and the child.

61
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:39,720
Jingyan, look at me.

62
00:06:40,320 --> 00:06:42,520
I said I never blamed you.

63
00:06:42,840 --> 00:06:44,840
If I hadn't been drawn into this life-and-death game,

64
00:06:44,840 --> 00:06:46,100
how could I have met you

65
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:47,800
and fallen in love with you?

66
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:50,760
This short time

67
00:06:51,200 --> 00:06:52,840
has been more wonderful

68
00:06:53,159 --> 00:06:54,600
and worthwhile

69
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:56,320
than all my previous years combined.

70
00:06:56,320 --> 00:06:59,000
I, Yan Qingshu, have no regrets in this life.

71
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:02,560
So don't blame yourself.

72
00:07:03,640 --> 00:07:04,600
I hope

73
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:06,480
I can see you happy

74
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:09,520
for the rest of my days.

75
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:10,720
Okay?

76
00:07:19,080 --> 00:07:19,720
Jingyan.

77
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:22,720
I want to take you back to Jingdu.

78
00:07:24,760 --> 00:07:25,360
Okay.

79
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:29,660
Look, Jingyan.

80
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:32,020
How bustling the streets are.

81
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:37,000
This is the peaceful and prosperous world your father

82
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:40,960
and the 3,000 soldiers of the Zhenbei Army protected with their lives.

83
00:07:40,960 --> 00:07:42,760
Their blood was not shed in vain.

84
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:44,840
Just like your father,

85
00:07:45,320 --> 00:07:48,920
you are a selfless hero who cares for the world.

86
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:51,620
We protected the land and the people.

87
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:55,060
Protected the lights of thousands of homes.

88
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:58,170
But the only one I couldn't protect

89
00:08:00,080 --> 00:08:02,360
was the person I wanted to protect the most.

90
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:02,920
Jingyan.

91
00:08:03,640 --> 00:08:06,320
Do you know what my lifelong wish is?

92
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:12,000
My wish used to be

93
00:08:12,520 --> 00:08:13,840
for my family's peace

94
00:08:14,200 --> 00:08:15,930
and my loved ones' well-being.

95
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:17,640
Now I have one more wish.

96
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,640
I hope

97
00:08:21,200 --> 00:08:22,400
that the one I love

98
00:08:23,080 --> 00:08:25,080
will be happy for the rest of his life

99
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:26,890
and free from pain forever.

100
00:09:40,640 --> 00:09:41,800
Life is like a dream,

101
00:09:42,560 --> 00:09:43,800
fleeting.

102
00:09:44,520 --> 00:09:46,980
Fortunately, in the last moments of my life,

103
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:49,720
having my beloved by my side

104
00:09:50,800 --> 00:09:51,930
is already perfect.

105
00:10:00,640 --> 00:10:01,960
For some reason,

106
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:05,200
I'm so sleepy right now.

107
00:10:07,160 --> 00:10:07,880
Maybe

108
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:10,600
you walked too much today

109
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:12,040
and got tired.

110
00:10:15,520 --> 00:10:16,780
I'll sleep for a while.

111
00:10:19,640 --> 00:10:20,300
Go to sleep.

112
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:09,600
Miss, you're finally awake.

113
00:11:15,680 --> 00:11:16,520
Xiaotao.

114
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:19,200
You must be tired from trying on the wedding dress yesterday.

115
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:20,930
You slept for four whole hours.

116
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:22,400
Strange.

117
00:11:22,760 --> 00:11:23,920
Look at the time.

118
00:11:24,520 --> 00:11:26,380
Why hasn't the groom arrived yet?

119
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:27,640
Groom?

120
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:31,060
Wedding dress?

121
00:11:40,480 --> 00:11:41,280
Miss.

122
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:45,250
Why are you looking at me like that?

123
00:12:00,040 --> 00:12:00,680
Miss.

124
00:12:02,280 --> 00:12:03,080
Xiaotao.

125
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:05,360
It's so good

126
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:06,640
to see you.

127
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:09,160
Okay.

128
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:11,080
Is everything in the manor ready?

129
00:12:11,400 --> 00:12:13,320
Make sure all the items to be prepared are accounted for,

130
00:12:13,320 --> 00:12:14,360
and don't miss the auspicious hour.

131
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:15,040
Yes, madam.

132
00:12:22,840 --> 00:12:23,520
Qingshu.

133
00:12:26,760 --> 00:12:28,620
This is a pair of concentric jade.

134
00:12:28,680 --> 00:12:30,640
You and Jingyan each hold half.

135
00:12:30,960 --> 00:12:33,680
This is the token of friendship between the Xiao and Yan families.

136
00:12:33,680 --> 00:12:34,440
Today,

137
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:35,880
I am giving it to you.

138
00:12:36,240 --> 00:12:37,840
Never let it leave your side.

139
00:12:38,800 --> 00:12:40,560
What are you two dawdling for?

140
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:48,120
Our Qingshu stealing the sugar jar when she was little

141
00:12:48,120 --> 00:12:49,120
and crying when she fell,

142
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:50,520
it feels like yesterday.

143
00:12:51,000 --> 00:12:53,660
In the blink of an eye, she's old enough to marry.

144
00:12:57,920 --> 00:12:59,640
Mother, Father.

145
00:13:00,400 --> 00:13:01,160
Xiaotao.

146
00:13:14,400 --> 00:13:16,330
The national mourning bell tolls.

147
00:13:17,040 --> 00:13:18,500
Could time have reversed,

148
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:21,240
returning to the day the late Emperor died?

149
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:27,320
Father, Mother.

150
00:13:34,400 --> 00:13:35,280
Pei Xuanlin.

151
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:38,480
Miss Yan, you recognize me?

152
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:44,000
Xiao Jingyan often told me

153
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:46,040
that he has a fierce general

154
00:13:46,160 --> 00:13:47,200
named Pei Xuanlin

155
00:13:47,640 --> 00:13:49,240
who is exceptionally brave.

156
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:52,320
Seeing you today, your aura is truly extraordinary.

157
00:13:52,960 --> 00:13:56,090
The Heir specifically ordered me to present this to you.

158
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:08,200
Xiao Jingyan.

159
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:10,610
What is the meaning of this?

160
00:14:11,040 --> 00:14:13,200
Miss Yan, the Heir entrusted me.

161
00:14:13,480 --> 00:14:14,680
The Emperor suddenly passed away.

162
00:14:14,680 --> 00:14:16,010
The court is turbulent.

163
00:14:16,040 --> 00:14:18,240
Quelling the rebellion in the palace this time,

164
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:19,600
his life or death is unpredictable.

165
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:21,200
If something happens to him,

166
00:14:21,760 --> 00:14:24,320
please find another good match.

167
00:14:24,880 --> 00:14:26,480
Don't ruin your life for him.

168
00:14:27,360 --> 00:14:28,690
He is quite thoughtful.

169
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:31,600
Why doesn't he arrange my afterlife properly?

170
00:14:31,800 --> 00:14:34,080
If he leaves me alone to face danger,

171
00:14:34,160 --> 00:14:36,690
from the highest heaven to the depths of hell,

172
00:14:37,200 --> 00:14:39,440
I, Yan Qingshu, will never let it go.

173
00:14:42,640 --> 00:14:44,440
Qingshu, calm down.

174
00:14:44,760 --> 00:14:47,000
Jingyan is thinking of your safety,

175
00:14:47,040 --> 00:14:48,300
with good intentions.

176
00:14:48,560 --> 00:14:49,840
How could you blame him?

177
00:14:49,840 --> 00:14:50,680
Mother.

178
00:14:51,520 --> 00:14:52,120
Father.

179
00:14:52,680 --> 00:14:55,320
Since I am promised to Xiao Jingyan,

180
00:14:56,040 --> 00:14:58,600
he is the only one in my life.

181
00:14:59,080 --> 00:15:01,940
We will share honor and disgrace, in life and death.

182
00:15:02,760 --> 00:15:03,680
I have no second thoughts.

183
00:15:03,680 --> 00:15:04,440
Good.

184
00:15:05,840 --> 00:15:07,720
This is truly a daughter of the Yan family.

185
00:15:07,720 --> 00:15:10,200
How could we abandon each other in times of crisis

186
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:12,130
and commit such a treacherous act?

187
00:15:12,160 --> 00:15:14,320
There is no such rule in the Yan family.

188
00:15:31,640 --> 00:15:32,370
Pei Xuanlin.

189
00:15:32,560 --> 00:15:33,560
Take me to see him.

190
00:15:33,560 --> 00:15:35,000
Right now, immediately!

191
00:16:01,320 --> 00:16:01,880
Cuimei.

192
00:16:01,960 --> 00:16:02,520
Cuimei.

193
00:16:03,760 --> 00:16:04,800
Yong.

194
00:16:05,440 --> 00:16:06,080
Wei, Kun, Hua, Chao.

195
00:16:06,080 --> 00:16:07,210
Wei, Kun, Hua, Chao.

196
00:16:08,440 --> 00:16:10,360
Long, Cong, Biao, Hao.

197
00:16:13,720 --> 00:16:14,320
Shuangbin.

198
00:16:14,280 --> 00:16:15,040
Ningzheng.

199
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:15,780
Ningzheng.

200
00:16:17,480 --> 00:16:20,040
Hao, Chun, Kang, Shuai, Hua.

201
00:16:22,480 --> 00:16:23,360
Weichao.

202
00:16:25,360 --> 00:16:26,800
Qiang, Yuan, Liang, Bo.

203
00:16:41,880 --> 00:16:42,140
- Xi.

204
00:16:42,200 --> 00:16:42,400
Xi.

205
00:16:42,880 --> 00:16:43,840
Xi.

206
00:16:43,920 --> 00:16:44,800
Taoqiang.

207
00:16:49,080 --> 00:16:49,480
Hui, Yue, Yun.

208
00:16:49,480 --> 00:16:50,610
Hui, Yue, Yun, Qing.

209
00:16:53,600 --> 00:16:54,720
Yiyi.
